Scalability: Sharding and Workchains allow TON to process transactions in parallel.

Speed: Near-instant transaction finality for real-world use cases.

Smart Contracts: Powered by TON Virtual Machine (TVM) for flexible and secure dApps.

Decentralized Services: TON Storage, TON DNS, and TON Payments for a complete ecosystem.

User-Friendly: Integration with Telegram for seamless wallet and dApp access.

